txt.en: Go and tell War-tyrant Akúlhun of your deeds
Do your part in the battle. Slay the Free People where they are found and earn your place in the army of Angmar!
As battle in the Ettenmoors is waged, you are recognized for your contribution to the slaughter.
Battle in the Ettenmoors continues and you must contribute to the fight.
'You are truly a warrior, [placeholder]. You are well remembered for these efforts.'
Brag of your deeds to War-tyrant Akúlhun
